The world of ''[[Game of Thrones]]'' has no overall or official name. Characters within the story simply refer to it as &quot;the world&quot;. At the time of the series, the known world consists of three discovered continents: [[Westeros]], [[Essos]], and [[Sothoryos]]. There are also numerous islands and archipelagos, including the [[Stepstones]], [[Summer Islands]], and [[Ibben|Ib]].
